<paragraph id="87B8661E26D1D06D45A9939B17C75FFC" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Type species.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="95D4DEA6391CD3D101528691FCE4C59D" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">
<taxonomicName id="42ECFF056D5F55EF08942821373CA5A7" authorityName="Eggers" authorityYear="1923" class="Lecanoromycetes" family="Stereocaulaceae" genus="Xyleborus" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Fungi" lsidName="Xyleborus insulindicus" order="Lecanorales" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" phylum="Ascomycota" rank="species" species="insulindicus">
<emphasis id="59C2D910ACA01B0D33FE1675066C3EC5" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Xyleborus insulindicus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Eggers, 1923; original designation.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="FB3BC9A5116CDC8808313219D266D99D" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph id="6B3E4FCFA2FDC915B528E62491D22546" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Diagnosis.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="BADDCB8925824CC736E2BB5D64F7ABCE" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">
Large and robust species, 4.1-5.6 mm long, 2.2-2.55
<normalizedToken id="68273EA8171E759C343FA497336A43F0" originalValue="Ã—">x</normalizedToken>
as long as wide. 
<taxonomicName id="406041770E3B4D679D2C768AE13F96B0" authority="Hulcr &amp; Cognato, 2009" authorityName="Hulcr &amp; Cognato" authorityYear="2009" class="Insecta" family="Curculionidae" genus="Beaverium" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Beaverium" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="F15579ACFED568853FC0DAE02CB426E5" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Beaverium</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is distinguished by the declivity distinctly flattened and posterolaterally broadened, posterolateral declivital margin costate, terminating at interstriae 5; pronotal disc asperate; pronotum anterior margin with continuously elevated carina; scutellum flat, flush with elytra, mycangial tufts absent, and procoxae contiguous.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="7392047B83748BEE9F6602081A746331" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" type="similar genera">
